


This document sketches the system of the Inari Saami verb.
For each stem type, it gives root vowels, stem vowels and alternations.


!!!Two-syllabic verbs

We have -âđ, -iđ, -eđ, -uđ, -ođ, as well as -eeđ, -oođ, -uuđ.

